<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Add event procedure</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-plus-square  "></i></span>).<br>
→ The window <strong>Create new event procedure</strong> opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a distinct name for the event procedure.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>event</strong> according to <a href="#event-procedure-update-order-status">Table 14</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
