<h2 id="6800">17. Setting up invoice generation for Amazon orders</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Invoices for your Amazon orders can be generated in different ways, depending on the settings you select in the <strong>Setup » Markets » Amazon »</strong> <em>Select the Amazon account</em> <strong>» Tab: Settings</strong>.</p>
</div>
